headline: 4 Stocks to Grab as Higher Industrial Production Boosts Manufacturing
summary: Industrial production jumps 0.7% as PMI hits 52.6, lifting outlook for PRLB, RBC, HLIO and TRMB amid rising orders and easing rates.
